<topic id="preferences-xquery-saxon">
  <title>Saxon-HE/PE/EE Preferences</title>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <keywords>
        <indexterm>Preferences<indexterm>Saxon-HE/PE/EE XQuery</indexterm></indexterm>
        <indexterm>Saxon HE/PE/EE XQuery preferences</indexterm>
      </keywords>
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <body>
    <p>To configure global options for XQuery transformation and validation scenarios that use the
        <uicontrol>Saxon HE/PE/EE</uicontrol> engine, <ph
        conkeyref="reusables-preferences-pages/open-the-preferences-page"/> and go to <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>XML</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>XSLT-XQuery</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>XQuery</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Saxon-HE/PE/EE</uicontrol>
      </menucascade>.</p>
    <p><ph keyref="product"/> allows you to configure the following XQuery options for the Saxon <ph
        keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Home Edition (HE), Professional Edition (PE), and Enterprise
      Edition (EE):<dl>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-use-config-file-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/optimization-level" id="optimization-level">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/linked-tree">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-recoverable-errors-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-strip-whitespaces-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p>The following option is available for Saxon <ph keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Professional
      Edition (PE) and Enterprise Edition (EE) only:<dl>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-allow-calls-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
    <p>The options available specifically for Saxon <ph keyref="saxon9FullVersion"/> Enterprise
      Edition (EE) are as follows:<dl>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-val-source-file-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/saxon-option-outval-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-querying-documents/xquery-enable-update-">
          <dt/>
          <dd/>
        </dlentry>
      </dl></p>
  </body>
